page.title: 07My family
page.content: I am Helen Moon I am 10 years old.my hobbies are rubber collecting ,tennis and swimming.My brother is called David Richard Moon and he has just passed his driving test he is 18 years old and he has a job in a garage. My two sisters are called Sian Louise Moon and Rebecca Clare Moon.Sian is 21 years old and Rebecca is 6.My dads name is Brian Roger Moon and my mums name is Diana Patricia Moon.My dad is the head master at St. Issey School.My mum teaches at Wadebridge Boys school.My dad is a steam train fan.All his walls in the house are plastered with Steam train posters.
